#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "Online Help"
msgstr "Ajuda en línia"

#. Tag: date
#: index.docbook:11
#, no-c-format
msgid "2018-04-01"
msgstr "1 d'abril de 2018"

#. Tag: releaseinfo
#: index.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid "Applications 18.04"
msgstr "Aplicacions 18.04"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:16
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On this page, you can find different ways to find online help and additional "
"information provided by the &kde; community."
msgstr ""
"En aquesta pàgina, descobrireu diferents maneres de trobar ajuda en línia i "
"informació addicional proveïda per la comunitat &kde;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kde; UserBase"
msgstr "&kde; UserBase"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/"
"An_introduction_to_KDE\">An Introduction to &kde;</ulink>&nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/An_introduction_to_KDE/ca\">Una "
"introducció al &kde;</ulink>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Learn more about the <ulink url=\"https://kde.org/community/whatiskde/\"> "
"&kde; community and its software</ulink> and find information to help you "
"get started. Also, discover what <ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/"
"Special:myLanguage/Welcome_to_KDE_UserBase\"> UserBase</ulink> is and how it "
"can help you."
msgstr ""
"Aprendre més quant a la <ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/What_is_KDE/ca"
"\">comunitat &kde; i el seu programari</ulink> i trobar informació per a "
"ajudar-vos a començar. A més, descobriu què és <ulink url=\"https://userbase."
"kde.org/Welcome_to_KDE_UserBase/ca\">UserBase</ulink> i com us pot ajudar."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/Getting_Help"
"\">Getting Help</ulink>&nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/Getting_Help/ca\">Obtenir ajuda</"
"ulink>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Need some help? Here are some suggested places where you can get help with "
"problems, as well some hints on how to improve the quality of answers you "
"receive."
msgstr ""
"Us cal ajuda? Aquests són alguns dels llocs suggerits, on podreu obtenir "
"ajuda amb els problemes, així com alguns suggeriments sobre com millorar la "
"qualitat de les respostes que rebreu."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/Applications"
"\">Applications</ulink>&nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/Applications/ca\">Aplicacions</"
"ulink>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Discover the wide variety of applications from the &kde; Community, and find "
"out what program suits your needs and preferences."
msgstr ""
"Descobriu la gran varietat d'aplicacions de la Comunitat &kde;, i quin "
"programa serà el més adequat a les vostres necessitats i preferències."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/Tutorials"
"\">Tutorials</ulink>&nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/Tutorials/ca\">Guies d'aprenentatge</"
"ulink>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"How-To's, Tips &amp; Tricks that can help make your &kde; software "
"experience more enjoyable and productive."
msgstr ""
"Com es fa, consells i trucs que us poden ajudar perquè l'experiència amb el "
"programari &kde; sigui més agradable i productiva."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kde; Forum"
msgstr "Fòrum del &kde;"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"https://forum.kde.org/\">&kde; Community Forums</ulink>&nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"https://forum.kde.org/\">Fòrums de la comunitat &kde;</"
"ulink>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &kde; Forums offer users, developers and people interested in &kde; a "
"place to help each other, discuss &kde;-related topics and exchange ideas. "
"You can find <ulink url=\"https://forum.kde.org/viewforum.php?f=14/"
"\">Tutorials &amp; Tips</ulink> in the forum."
msgstr ""
"Els fòrums del &kde; ofereixen als usuaris, desenvolupadors i persones "
"interessades en el &kde; un lloc per a ajudar-nos els uns als altres, "
"debatre temes relacionats amb el &kde; i intercanviar idees. Podeu trobar-hi "
"<ulink url=\"https://forum.kde.org/viewforum.php?f=14/\">Guies "
"d'aprenentatge i consells</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kde; Techbase"
msgstr "&kde; Techbase"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "<ulink url=\"https://techbase.kde.org/\">&kde; Techbase</ulink>&nbsp;"
msgstr "<ulink url=\"https://techbase.kde.org/\">&kde; Techbase</ulink>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Information for developers and help to set up a &kde; development "
"environment."
msgstr ""
"Informació per a desenvolupadors i ajuda per a crear un entorn de "
"desenvolupament del &kde;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kde; Documentation"
msgstr "Documentació del &kde;"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"https://docs.kde.org/\">&kde; Documentation site</ulink>&nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"https://docs.kde.org/\">Lloc de documentació per al &kde;</"
"ulink>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This page holds the complete &kde; User Documentation in over 25 languages "
"for the released and the development version of &kde-frameworks;, &plasma-"
"workspaces; and &applications;."
msgstr ""
"Aquesta pàgina conté tota la documentació d'usuari del &kde; en més de 25 "
"idiomes per a la versió publicada i la de desenvolupament del &kde-"
"frameworks;, &plasma-workspaces; i &applications;."
